Universe of Goo Milestone 2
by Vismay and Kaivan

How to compile our code?
 - Open up the goo.pro file in QtCreator and hit build

Creative Components:
	- Beach theme with water, sand and sky gradients
	- Particles are now beach balls with multiple colors
	- Clouds can be turned on/off through the UI
		-clouds move and are auto-regenerated when they move off the screen
	-Game Mode
		-start with a special Golden Particle
		-using any means possible, try to get the Golden Particle into one of the 2 boxes on the screen
		-if the golden particle reaches the box, you win the game
		-if the golden particle is destroyed or leaves the screen, you lose the game
